Project Description
At Digital Interaction Group we develop Microsoft .NET Gadgeteer modules, code and example projects.

We put up the source code for new modules and projects here, so that everyone can have fun with Gadgeteer.

  • DMX (Planned)
  • VISCA Camera Control (Planned)
  • Websockets (Planned)
  • STOMP (Planned)
